The paper discusses cutting-edge botnet features and detection strategies, which are primarily related to computer security (cs.CR) and networking (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper may touch upon artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC) as botnets often use these technologies. Finally, the paper may also discuss software engineering (cs.SE) as botnets are complex software systems.
